Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:03.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:07.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,囤货不是为了过年的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:12.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说是为了过年时店铺休业而储备的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:14.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:17.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,全部都空了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:18.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是个只要零食还有剩就会吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:24.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,存不起货的坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:29.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好了各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:33.88,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&H3C465D&\move(1296,786,1210,786)}6号刊终审
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:33.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,6号刊份的终审完后  年内的工作也就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:35.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把元旦后截稿的7号刊调到年内的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以放假到这天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:43.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能放这么长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把7号刊的份也画了放假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:50.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在年内把7号刊的份也给画好攒起来  好好过年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:57.28,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}懒散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:00.03,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(1000,0)}空闲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:02.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说好的攒进度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:05.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家都还在等着老师的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请再认真点干
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,认真的漫画家  怎么可能会去攒进度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:16.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只要时间还有剩就会最大限度地去提高质量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:17.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才算真正的漫画家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:21.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:26.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是个只要还有剩时间就会懒惰下去的坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就知道会变成这样…
