Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有在深刻地反省
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:03.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反省什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没忍住吃掉了储备的零食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作为自发的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我把很难的汉字抄写了一百遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人…人各有所短
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以其实没必要那么在意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:23.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,既然已经接受惩罚了那就再买些回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸你也太惯着女儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:34.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样下去会变成没有计划性的大人哦
