Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要去试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是头奖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:15.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以和宠物一起温泉旅行的三天两晚的旅行券
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,恭喜您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这儿  是人气旅店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,洛克也能一起去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.29,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H565551&\frx18\fry356\frz16.78\pos(896,188.8)\org(897.6,259.2)}和宠物一起温泉旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.29,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H565551&\frx8\fry0\frz17.71\pos(1048,636.8)\org(1054.4,705.6)}使用期限  1月6日~1月末
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.29,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord2\c&H565551&\fscx91\fscy97\frz17.66\frx6\fry358\pos(1116.8,945.6)\org(1155.2,1011.2)}※需要预约  {\fs50}使用本券时请务必提前与我们联系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:27.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,无论如何都得在年内干完7号刊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:40.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是一旦下定决心就一定会做到的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不愧是老师  好汉该出手时就出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,已确认收下7号刊的原稿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我预约了要去夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以还在担心要是完不成该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.10,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僵住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,夏威夷？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,三个月之前就预约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还真是让人捏了一把汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在那时候我还没给你说过要画七号刊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我觉得您多半会画
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这种事情早点讲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为要是讲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说不定就会故意不画让我去不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人类还没有堕落到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:23.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:29.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,听了这事后干劲低落最终导致画不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看吧果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在这期间我也要去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:36.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师也要去旅行么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以呢  是要去哪儿旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:41.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,伊豆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,伊豆  挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不过我是去夏威夷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是这种地方会让人干劲低落的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为啥  我的确是要去夏威夷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,相较于漫画家拼命换来的假期  3天2晚的小旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.83,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&HE45458&\frz18.8\pos(592,244.8)}箱根温泉\N\h{\fs40}2天1晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.83,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord3\pos(1190.667,420.8)\frz296.8\c&H7067CB&}热海旅行  3天2晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.83,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H2024AD&\frz82.51\pos(1246.933,318.933)}亲子温泉旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.83,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\frz343.9\pos(681.333,433.334)\c&H60C5E7&}当日回归
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙随随便便就是去海外度假一周
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.96,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H39CDE3&\3c&H000000&\move(89.6,219.2,308.4,220.8,0,2859)}泰国曼谷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.96,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H71EFF6&\3c&H2B6B55&\frz31.55\move(408,785.6,631.2,782,0,2859)}夏威夷火奴鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.96,kakushigoto in 12,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frz340.2\c&H44C4D5&\3c&H1F1610&\move(992,334.4,1201.6,337.6,0,2859)}瑞士{\c&H4A34CD&}阿尔卑斯{\c&HFFFFFF&}之旅  {\c&HF3E9E5&}5天6晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿也完成了  假期也有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对漫画家来说  预定长期旅行是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:12.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道会不会因为什么麻烦导致原稿画不完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz18.5\pos(267.2,148.8)\c&H3C3948&}随身带美工刀被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H3C3948&\pos(1118.4,48)}助手逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H3C3948&\pos(272,904)\frz8.946}沉迷动森
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H3C3948&\frz6.601\pos(681.6,681.6)}座椅弹簧跳出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H3C3948&\pos(1169.6,736)}因为打雷使工作地点停电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便在年内画好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.98,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\pos(1088,208)}啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.98,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz278.3\pos(518.4,212.8)}这个拿去改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,卡在明年初的终审需要重交的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还必须要从旅行的地方回来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,特别是黄段子呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以只有能马上回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「安·近·短」的选项
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.44,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：安在日语中有便宜的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在跨年时期去海外度假的漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,全部都是垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且  漫画家在跨年时期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不能随便制定计划最大的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:39.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那便是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,必然会得感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真会说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,放假把一年份的病都给消化了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿攒不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,病倒是攒起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明职场庆功宴都还没举办…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,职场上的人员在这儿我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但为什么你们也在这儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:09.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,普通地来探病了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,布丁的话吃得下么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事  课长只是单纯的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  部长只是单纯的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们先统一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,别担心  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,旅行之前我一定会好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,旅行是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抽奖中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,伊豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且还带螃蟹自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:42.31,kakushigoto in 8,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs65\c&HCA7DE2&\3c&H411EB6&\frz21.21\pos(380.8,403.2)}和宠物一起{\c&H5777E3&}温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:42.31,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&H3B15CA&\frz30.95\pos(1513.6,793.6)}螃蟹{\c&H2F2C48&\bord0}自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:43.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,螃蟹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:48.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道是因为姬写了很多「蟹」字才中奖的么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,写愿望原来有效果的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是像吸引法则一样的么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对了  为了让孩子他爸早点好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家一起来写愿望祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要写什么字比较好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要写愿望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抄经文不是挺好的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:18.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打扰了  从编辑部回来后就来晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…这熟人满聚一堂的感觉是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道说老师他…病危了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,经…经文？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  您要去世了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去世？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为病危才会聚了这么多人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:45.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是么…原来我是病危啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呀  经文这不都给准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是大家  都说只是单纯的感冒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会对本人说出真相啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师您快挂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…你给我适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,死而复生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬要是当真了该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤老师  还不能勉强起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看吧真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请不要乱来啊老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,死虽然是死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是可能要休刊一次左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到那时候就说「作者去取材了」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「作者犯死罪了」是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,无论如何都想要一死么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没问题吗  在姬面前说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事的  她似乎因为担心而累倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,烧也基本上退了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是因为抄经文起效了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然写愿望挺灵的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:57.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,病已经好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是啊  烧也退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:04.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能按计划去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然写愿望挺灵的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,写愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.09,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an9}要结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.09,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,结婚成就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.09,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}脱单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,写愿望真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…这是诅咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被思慕的人也挺可怜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:32.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,靠着抽奖中的旅行券  我们正在前往温泉旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直都挺在意一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:45.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父亲和女儿的二人旅行  会被人怎么看待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.25,kakushigoto in 8,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H62676B&\pos(313.6,382.4)}小汪之家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,恭候已久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤先生  请问是三位么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是  是两…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  是三人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:10:59.88,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz284.4\move(1273.6,417.6,1275,358)}洛克？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是三人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:06.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是么  这种地方狗也要算一人么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我还以为是以妈妈在为前提问的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能带狗狗住的和式房间真是少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这就是这家旅店的特色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然我们对温泉也很有自信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被称作是德川家的隐藏温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,隐藏温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,隐藏温泉是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:34.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概是不会被其他人找到的而隐藏的温泉…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:39.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要藏着  让大家都泡泡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:45.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说起来  温泉旅馆给人一种「隐瞒之事」很多的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正如  婚外恋的幽会场所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或是政治家躲避媒体的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.27,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(871.6,762.6)}客房负责人  莎拉波娃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:59.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或者是不要询问工作人员的过往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:12:00.40,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}莎拉波娃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,洛克  不要叫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在这里你要做一个绅士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也许是隔壁房间也有狗狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.04,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1459.2,244.8)}正在改装中  不可使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又或是出过事的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:29.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,温泉  温泉  吃饭之前泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我稍微有些担心温泉浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,让她一个人的话我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但一起的话我更担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:41.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是想稍微看下她的情况我就会被立即逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这种时候我到底该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:45.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:50.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如此为女儿着想的我  怎么可能没预料到这种情况会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:51.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:53.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真没想到你会把我们叫来女浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能够免费来泡温泉倒是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但您为什么这么担心泡温泉这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:02.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你知道有多少日本人是死在泡温泉的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且  还有那些可恶漫画家画的温泉段子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我全是些不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜托了  帮我照看好姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:14.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是发生了什么  我们会立即通知您的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,诶…姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:23.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我泡得好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你已经泡好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我有些担心洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸你慢慢泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您不来偷窥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们可都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要再说这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.22,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(955.2,265.6)}正在改装中  不可使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然很让人在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:51.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.98,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frx0\fry14\frz269.1\pos(176,496)\org(448,571.2)}正在改装中  不可使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这间房间是不是什么出过事的禁忌房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  并不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们正准备将其改造成展示室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,展示室？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这里曾是文豪田端康成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.82,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：源自现实文豪川端康成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,写出「伊豆的罗勒」的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.70,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：源自川端康成所著「伊豆的舞女」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:11.74,kakushigoto in 2 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,0)\fs45\frz299\c&H65748D&\move(480,166.4,641.2,150.4,0,6572)}不是芥末  而是罗勒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来就是在这个房间写出那部名作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来如此  是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,螃蟹  好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这间旅馆总感觉背后隐藏着好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我已经不想再继续隐瞒下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我会向我老婆坦白然后离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和你正大光明地结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…这个真的很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:42.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他是因为料理太过好吃深受感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  蛭贺尾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实我也有隐瞒着的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:54.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我其实并不是26岁而是40岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:58.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且还离了两次婚欠了500万
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事的  谢谢你告诉我这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也隐瞒了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你生日时我送给你的这只狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实并不是吉娃娃而是杂种狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,吉娃娃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我已经唯它不可了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,品种什么的怎么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是谢谢你能够告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能够说出来  我也觉得轻松了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,任何狗狗都很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正是  我反对犬种歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:32.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实我对老婆你也有隐瞒之事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:37.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实我也隐瞒着我早就发现你隐瞒着的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:40.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,各位觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在时机正好  将自己的隐瞒之事说出来会很轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实我已经被裁员了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我每天都装作去上班其实都是在公园里打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实住宿这间旅馆的钱我用的是公款  而我却隐瞒了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:01.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实我的眼睛  鼻子  嘴巴和下巴都是整容过的  而我却隐瞒着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实大家刚才吃的伊豆高原牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:10.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是从我听也没听过的国家进口的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这什么情节展开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下来轮到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  我并没有什么隐瞒之事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:21.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来吧  将你的隐瞒之事说出来  和我们一起轻松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:25.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来一同解脱吧  将隐瞒之事舍去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:30.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}来吧  来吧  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这协同的压迫感究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:36.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}来吧  来吧  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的隐瞒之事是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:49.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:52.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,房间里好像有什么黑影在动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:58.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不想再隐瞒下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实  这间房间里有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会出现田端康成老师的鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:13.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,每晚都在写着未完结的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说出来  我也痛快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有隐瞒之事真是太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.10,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,730.6)}客房负责人  莎拉波娃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:26.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那你的莎拉波娃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找到了  田端康成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在旅馆写作时突然吐血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,之后在医院去世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,吐血和殉情之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以前文豪们的故事都挺有戏剧色彩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且人物形象也都挺鲜明的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:44.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像这样作者的鲜明特点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是造就了作品的评价的一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:50.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果我也吐血  是不是我的漫画就能卖出去更多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:54.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,黄段子漫画家吐血也只会被耻笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,基本上像吐血这样正经的疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对搞笑漫画家来说是负面影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,读者可就笑不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说起来  您用您的裸照塑造自己的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不也是一种对真相的伪装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对不起  只是我的想象而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不然你也不会做那么蠢的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你真是说得好让人伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嘘  你会吵醒姬的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不能去那里  洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是洛克被带到魔界了  姬会很伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有鬼  没有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:47.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:53.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,麝香猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来这家伙就是文豪的真面目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:01.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,布置还是和当初一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是在这张书桌前完成了那部名作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是真有文豪的鬼魂的话  我倒是想被它附上身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,保佑我成为人气漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就这么一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个时间应该不会被人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你个笨蛋  怎么可能有幽灵什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有很多人看见过的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:27.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我绝对要拍到幽灵的照片  然后拿到很多赞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:30.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是那间房间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:41.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看  见  了  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:49.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,听说昨晚幽灵出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:50.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  早晨这件事就闹得挺厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬你不怕幽灵之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我当然也很怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:04.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  我想如果他们能够存在的话比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:10.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果在的话  幽灵的数量就会很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:15.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实  如果死去的人都变成了幽灵  那数量就很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,地球可就装不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:22.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以它们才是透明的  和它们撞上也能穿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不能够触碰它们也是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看  前段时间的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7A5E59&\bord2\frx10\fry0\org(105.6,372.8)\pos(321.6,340.8)\frz20.28}出现了？文豪幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H7A5E59&\frx10\fry0\frz20.28\pos(443.2,553.6)\org(227.2,585.6)}由加里的旅馆疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord2\c&H7A5E59&\frx10\fry0\frz24.02\pos(992,944)\org(776,976)}附近学生所拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H7A5E59&\frx8\fry358\frz24.82\pos(1153.6,956.8)\org(1115.2,982.4)}「小汪之家」出现幽灵骚动就在旅馆附近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的超可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不过这个文豪幽灵身上没什么气场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.30,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(1665.6,390.4)\frz273.7\c&HAD93FF&\3c&H7E3FDF&}点赞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父亲他有这么一个习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:50.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,每每遇到讨厌和烦恼的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他总会从外廊进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那天父亲回来后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了不让我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说是自己工作能力提高了  被别家公司挖过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有了一份更好的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:09.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但我察觉到了那是他自己辞去了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:15.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那时他辞去的原来就是这份画画工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么他不愿意继续了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:23.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然他本人写的是卖不出去了不想继续了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但你也知道并不是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是他自己不愿意再动笔了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样说  听上去比较帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实他是画不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤老师也对读者有着隐瞒之事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:41.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为他无论怎么画都不能让读者笑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这事你也不用专门说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤老师又没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:51.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但将作者和作品分开来看待的人很少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:52.28,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(1100,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frz350.4\pos(160,73.6)\3c&H30323F&}8人失踪。持续搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:52.28,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(1100,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frz351.9\pos(1017.6,224)\3c&H2D303D&}事故现场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,悲惨的私生活被人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:58.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对搞笑漫画家来说是致命伤
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
