Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:36.12,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}将离别的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:45.92,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}ポケットに匿していたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:45.92,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}隐藏在口袋中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:53.01,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}想い出は  モノクローム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:53.01,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}回忆是单色相片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:58.52,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}色を点けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:58.52,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}给我点上颜色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:06.82,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}もう一度  そばに来て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:06.82,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}再一次来到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:11.82,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}はなやいで  うるわしの Color Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:11.82,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}花枝招展的  美丽的Color Girl
