Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:34.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,风之紧身裤还有十周就将完结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我原以为这样的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:41.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能够一直持续下去
